  "texts": [
    "In total, 45 tissue samples were collected: From each of the three accessions, three biological replicates were taken from each of: young leaf, root, stem, flag leaf and inflorescence.",
    "Samples were collected at the same time of day at approximately 5-6 h after daylight.",
    "The seedling leaves and roots were harvested after two weeks of recovery in the original growth chamber and rinsed with water to remove soil particles.",
    "When the plants had 4-5 tillers, the stems, flag leaves and inflorescences were harvested together.",
    "The green inflorescences were collected immediately after pollination."
  ],
